text.section:
As part of the verdict in any action for damages for personal injury in which the cause of action arises on or after July 1, 1986 or for wrongful death in which the cause of action arises on or after October 1, 1994, the trier of fact shall itemize the award to reflect the monetary amount intended for:
Past medical expenses;
Future medical expenses;
Past loss of earnings;
Future loss of earnings;
Noneconomic damages; and
Other damages.
